{"tid":1415190,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"留意前線義士心理健康","createTime":"2019-08-05T13:20:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T16:02:48.000Z","uid":255280,"like":39,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c0f7bfeeefc0d5f65571c66f508fc79973a887cd","tid":1415190,"uid":255280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:20:44.000Z","msg":"近日發現有人提出要殺狗洩憤，而當其他人想勸說既時間就俾人話:「冷氣軍師」「未去過前線唔好講咁多」之類既回應。<br />\n       我對此表示完全理解，當自己身邊既人俾狗圍毆，見到女義士俾狗非禮，聽到義士係狗屋俾狗虐待，我地作為同路人，無一不憤慨，尤其係每一次都係前線目睹一切既義士。<br />\n        我相信當我地俾緊壓力黑警，等佢地精神崩潰既同時，一直接收極大量負面情緒既前線義士，都一樣係崩潰邊緣。故此，我希望大家停下互相指責，與其話前放火乜乜乜，玩丫叉乜乜乜，不如俾個機會，俾啲時間前線好好休息，休息是為了走更遠的路。<br />\n       亦希望各方重拾互相尊重，不割席不分化既宗旨去打呢道仗。<br />\nBe Water,Be Humble <br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"5c949695de23eb3a754dc0470274c533dc43d55d","tid":1415190,"uid":255280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:22:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光</span></span>"},{"pid":"5361c34aecdd753a31fcee419f8727cf5594af84","tid":1415190,"uid":255280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:23:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">復</span></span></span>"},{"pid":"28ee18aa5c733c98b5c2c09f5456c5b59d86c909","tid":1415190,"uid":222907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:23:20.000Z","msg":"on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39cde14328764b97fd9109421977a5ecf5246f82","tid":1415190,"uid":255280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:23:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">香</span></span>"},{"pid":"47b5493cbed739dd881eb7bc89ab7921c07a7963","tid":1415190,"uid":255280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:23:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">港</span></s